               stealing a pair of silver shoe buckles, value 10 s. a pair of silver knee buckles, value 5 s. a silver stock buckle, value 3 s. two pair of silver sleeve buttons, value 2 s. one hundred pieces of foreign coin called Rupees, value 9 l. nine guineas, and a half guinea
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17770910-30-victim323" type="victimName">
